\subsection*{Noisewords}
The \texttt{ID} tokens lexeme is not allowed to match any the following noisewords independent of the casing:\\\\
\texttt{is}
\texttt{and}
\texttt{or}
\texttt{mod}
\texttt{if}
\texttt{then}
\texttt{else}
\texttt{end}
\texttt{random}
\texttt{of}
